query:
SELECT
            DATE(created_at) as "date!",
            COUNT(*) as "count!: i64"
        FROM points_transactions
        WHERE DATE(created_at) >= $1 AND DATE(created_at) <= $2
            AND (type::text = 'stay' OR type::text = 'booking')
        GROUP BY DATE(created_at)
        ORDER BY DATE(created_at)
